title: Jharkhand football team
text:
The Jharkhand football team (<a href="Hindi%20Language">Hindi</a>:झारखंड फुटबॉल टीम) is an Indian <a href="association%20football">football</a> team representing <a href="Jharkhand">Jharkhand</a> in the <a href="Santosh%20Trophy">Santosh Trophy</a>.
They have never won the Santosh trophy. They failed to qualify for the final rounds of 73rd Santosh Trophy (2015).
